Package com.day.commons.datasource.poolservice

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataSourcePool
    Combines multiple DataSourcePoolProvider services into a single service that gives access to preconfigured data sources.
    DataSourcePoolProvider
    Used by DataSourcePool to provide data sources of a single type (for example a JDBC DataSource or an LDAPDataSource).
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DataSourceNotFoundException
    Indicate that no datasource could be found with the required name.
    TypeNotAvailableException
    Indicates that the required type of data source is not available.
